# IBus Zhuyin Input Method

## Introduction

ibus-zhuyin - a phonetic (Zhuyin/Bopomofo) Chinese input method for Traditional Chinese characters with phrase support, predictive text, Hsu's keyboard layout, visual symbol keyboard, and advanced punctuation modes.

## Compile and install manually

    $ git clone https://github.com/fourdollars/ibus-zhuyin.git && cd ibus-zhuyin
    $ ./autogen.sh
    $ ./configure --prefix=/usr --libexecdir=/usr/lib/ibus CFLAGS=-g CXXFLAGS=-g
    $ make
    $ sudo make install
    $ ibus-daemon -r -d -x

